title: Emanuel Xavier to deliver Hispanic Heritage Month and LGBT History Month talk (Ohio University)
text: ( Source : Ohio University ) Oct 9, 2015 By Aunjanna Million Emanuel Xavier , who is a poet, spoken word artist, novelist, editor, and activist, will speak about his life in honor of Hispanic Heritage Month and LGBT History Month at 7 p.m.
